00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:16,000
(Watch on www.kisskh.xyz Support Admin)

2
00:00:17,726 --> 00:00:19,519
HONG MIN-BEOM

3
00:00:19,602 --> 00:00:20,770
Hello?

4
00:00:20,854 --> 00:00:22,647
Yeah, I'll be there in ten minutes.

5
00:00:22,731 --> 00:00:24,983
Director Hong, don't hang up the phone.

6
00:00:25,525 --> 00:00:27,193
Just flip it over
and leave it on the table,

7
00:00:27,277 --> 00:00:28,111
