8
00:00:28,194 --> 00:00:30,447
- You get what I'm saying, right?

9
00:00:39,330 --> 00:00:40,749
Let me cut to the chase.

10
00:00:42,876 --> 00:00:44,169
What are you doing?

11
00:00:49,674 --> 00:00:51,926
Stop being a little bitch and sit still.

12
00:00:52,010 --> 00:00:53,178
GANG-YONG

13
00:00:53,261 --> 00:00:54,095
You there?

14
00:00:54,179 --> 00:00:56,431
I'm right here, asshole.
What the hell are you trying to do?

15
00:00:56,514 --> 00:00:57,932
Do you have a death wish?

16
00:00:59,434 --> 00:01:02,729
You're making a big fucking mistake
right now, you stupid fucking asshole.

17
00:01:02,812 --> 00:01:05,273
You might want to tell him to shut up.

18
00:01:05,356 --> 00:01:07,609
Dude! Stop!

19
00:01:07,692 --> 00:01:09,819
You're going to rot in a cell
for the rest of your life.

20
00:01:09,903 --> 00:01:10,779
You motherfucker!

21
00:01:12,405 --> 00:01:14,949
Fuck! Shut the hell up,
you fucking son of a bitch!

22
00:01:17,702 --> 00:01:19,120
Jackass.

23
00:01:21,372 --> 00:01:22,832
Have you calmed down?

24
00:01:25,627 --> 00:01:26,669
